Package org.apache.calcite.sql.parser

Class SqlParserTest

java.lang.Object
org.apache.calcite.sql.parser.SqlParserTest
public class SqlParserTest extends Object
A SqlParserTest is a unit-test for the SQL parser.

To reuse this test for an extension parser, implement the parserImplFactory() method to return the extension parser implementation.

    SqlParserTest.Sql
    Helper class for building fluent code such as sql("values 1").ok();.
    protected class 
    SqlParserTest.SqlList
    Helper class for building fluent code, similar to SqlParserTest.Sql, but used to manipulate a list of statements, such as sqlList("select * from a;").ok();.

    Default implementation of SqlParserTest.Tester.
    class 
    SqlParserTest.UnparsingTesterImpl
    Implementation of SqlParserTest.Tester which makes sure that the results of unparsing a query are consistent with the original query.
